g.text: Divide the problem into sub problem solve it individually and combine the result.
Sn stands for sub problem solution, can be run parallel.
S stands for combine of sub problem solution
Must have condition :- Data structure must be sorted.
Element can be accessed in a constant amount of time.
Two approach can be used as followed :-
Iterative binary search algorithm :- Execute while loop and continue process of comparing the key and splitting the search space in halves
Recursive binary search algorithm :- Create recursive function to and compare the key with middle of search space,
if key found return index, otherwise return index to execute next search space.
low = mid + 1, high will remain same.
